The balcony of the villa has been carpeted, and the Prince will sit out longer to-day than he has since the operation.

abstract: The other day, writes a Naples correspondent, at Genoa, in the presence of the special and royal delegate, Pavesi, the chest was opened in which was preserved the celebrated violin of Nicolo Paganini. Afterward Paganini's violin was deposited in a case covered by a glass shade.

abstract: MOBILE, Ala., March 30.--Passenger train No. 1 of the Louisville and Nashville, which left Montgomery Tuesday, arrived here this afternoon at 3 o'clock. The train was detained three days at Evergreen by wash-outs above and below that place. The drummers on board formed a baseball nine and had several lively games with the men of Evergreen.

abstract: CHICAGO, March 30.--This morning found the prospects for more trouble in the Chicago, Burlington and Quincy strike as promising as the worst enemies of the road and of the men could wish.
